unds. For comparison, in the\nmore stringent CONGEST model, the best deterministic algorithm for constructing\na $(2k-1)$-spanner with $O(kn^{1+1/k})$ edges runs in $O(n^{1-1/k})$ rounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2016 20:16:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-09"}
