recy capacity. In addition, the impact of imperfect channel state\ninformation on the performance of our proposed protocol is also investigated.\nNumerical results validate all theoretical analyses and reveal the merits of\nthe proposed AnJ protocol over its half-duplex counterpart.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Aug 2016 12:05:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-15"}
